Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.59,0:32:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是ALPHA-1 风太大听不见！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.69,0:32:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待情况好转时再跟你们联络
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.73,0:32:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 这家伙想打架吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.43,0:32:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.76,0:32:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALPHA-1 OMEGA-1
