Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.91,0:32:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.83,0:33:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这简直就是在玩摔角
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.32,0:34:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没子弹了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.08,0:34:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完蛋了！废物！
